OL,5,G1205 Outback Truckers
OL,6,     FIt's mid-afternoon in Perth and
OL,7,     FDion's super size convoy is
OL,8,     Fpushing hard to get out of the
OL,9,     Fcity before sunset. And the fate
OL,10,     Fof Steve's trip hangs on one phone
OL,11,     Fcall to his mechanic.
OL,12,G1300 Outback Truckers
OL,13,     FOver the last three days, Steve
OL,14,     FGrahame has hauled 130 tonnes of
OL,15,     Ffreight a massive 2000 km, and his
OL,16,     Ftruck's taken a beating. Under the
OL,17,     Fbonnet the news isn't good.
OL,18,G1400 Outback Truckers
OL,19,     FA driver travels through an area
OL,20,     Fwhere bush fire has run wild. An
OL,21,     Fowner operator faces the busiest
OL,22,     Fweek of his career.
